# Chicago Crash Data Dashboard

Interactive Tableau dashboard analyzing fatal crash patterns in Chicago through trend analysis, time-of-day distributions, and geographic visualization.

## Dashboard Features
- Fatal crash trends over time
- Time-of-day crash analysis
- Geographic mapping of crash locations
- Interactive filters and dashboard exploration

## Tools Used
- Tableau
- Excel
- Chicago Data Portal datasets

## Objective
The goal of this project was to use data visualization techniques to identify patterns and communicate insights related to traffic safety and crash trends in Chicago.
